{"tid":1838513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"花樣年旗下【星晨旅遊】取消新春期間出發中國旅行團","createTime":"2020-01-24T05:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T05:00:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"88ca2a63875a63e68bd05a1321eeeb8953bc5176","tid":1838513,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:00:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504608-20200124.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504608-20200124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=546c14ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504608-20200124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ea617d7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504608-20200124.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n因應內地感染新型冠狀病毒的肺炎疫情擴散，本港多間旅行社相繼取消新春期間，出發往內地的旅行團。<br />\n<br />\n星晨旅遊亦表示，取消年初一至初七期間出發的全線中國旅行團，以保障顧客和員工健康，並將有專人主動聯絡受影響旅客。"}]}